                        <tr>
                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Another tip for new players:
<br />

<br />
If you are forming an instance group and someone says "I will come but only if item_01 is reserved for me", you are better off finding someone else.  This isn't extremely common.  However, my experience is that such people will either:
<br />

<br />
1. Depart immediately upon getting what they want
<br />
2. Depart immediately at the first sign of any trouble (someone disconnects or makes a mistake)
<br />
3. End up rolling on everything whether they can use it or not (I'm rolling for my friend/relative/alt who is Mage/Shaman/Engineer/Enchanter/etc.).</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><span style="color: darkblue"> 
<br />
<a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=831098" target="_blank" class="postlink">Nokei Orhaste &lt;Retired&gt; E66.191/L h++ 2.8khp 4.6km ft12 BK10</a></span>
