                                <td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Qinweni, basically, if you damage a mob first, you'll get the exp.  There's no way to kill steal after you damage it first.  You would have to abandon the mob (i.e. run away) for someone else to get exp.  Thus, anyone coming up and beating on things you have clearly already attacked is simply helping you.</span><span class="postbody"><br />_________________<br /><a href="http://wow.allakhazam.com/profile.html?37749" target="_blank" class="postlink"><img src="http://www.blaynesucks.com/images/Bellanfear.gif" border="0" /></a>
